game.name: Club Sandwich
game.description:
Cooking is the best thing you can do to make your hungry tummy satisfied. Today we have brought to you a brand new girls game where you are going to play the role of a chef who is expert in sandwich making. Your popularity has made it possible for you to attend a wide range of customers from multiple locations across the city. Are you ready to accept this challenge? Join Club Sandwich and be prepared to challenge your sharp reflexes and complete all burger orders on time to score!

Try to prepare as many burgers as you can to please all your clients and complete your game with the maximum score possible in this HTML5 cooking game! It is really an honor to run a popular sandwich restaurant. And, your responsibility gets increased when you take care of it during the festival Coachella. Get ready to attend people from all across the city and help them to eat your famous sandwiches! Try to react fast otherwise, you would lose your customers in this fun sandwich puzzle!

This restaurant game is meant for players from different age groups and equipped with matchless characteristics that can keep you glued to the screen for long. There are 100 unique and challenging levels to explore and 300 stars to collect. Prepare the ingredients by touching the screen and prepare a maximum number of score! Play more popular titles from the category of free cooking games that are worth exploring to beat your time and have unlimited fun without download! Good luck to prepare more sandwiches and become the master of fast foods!
